{"tid":691963,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"地產經紀「跑唔夠數」　自罰街上當頭淋水","createTime":"2018-06-06T08:00:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-06T08:23:34.000Z","uid":39464,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ef9e6dcad23cecf44bef03763eef471a71567904","tid":691963,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T08:00:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180606/s00004/47ab3afabd411d5b8954f9cf04c50ceb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180606%2Fs00004%2F47ab3afabd411d5b8954f9cf04c50ceb.jpg&h=f71e73f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n廣西桂林一名女地產經紀，因未能完成每月業績目標關係，竟在街上當頭淋水，以此自罰。片段流傳後，惹起內地網民熱議。<br />\n<br />\n從片段中所見，該名女地產經紀大喊：「沒有完成任務，接受懲罰！」同時另一員工從女經紀頭頂淋下一桶水，其間女經紀還不忘大喊數次「堅決完成」。<br />\n<br />\n片段流傳後，惹起內地網民熱議。有內地傳媒事後訪問有關地產中介行，負責人稱公司員工每月都會自定小目標，若完成不了便自願懲罰，強調有關行徑屬自發行為。他又透露，該女經紀日常工作很認真，業績非常好，「只是她定的目標比別人高，就是為了表達自己的一個決心」。<br />\n<br />\n除淋水外，該公司員工還會以吃苦瓜、吃芥末，或跑十公里等方式來激勵自己。負責人坦言：「可能在外人看來這很瘋狂，但我覺得這挺正常的，做銷售的人對自己應該有這樣的決心。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180606/s00004/1528268064887\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180606%2Fs00004%2F1528268064887&d=TTCSStd0SLCqKvy40WHKmhOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=c6f0bbed\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180606%2Fs00004%2F1528268064887&h=0c777d04\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180606/s00004/1528268064887</a>"},{"pid":"1b66cd1344d9055c7a4f2eb82a348cab394a6eea","tid":691963,"uid":147146,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T08:08:18.000Z","msg":"呢個樣 難怪唔夠數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8342d5efa402fc184d53fe666b4f61f7c3d9e5a9","tid":691963,"uid":87428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T08:13:06.000Z","msg":"Rice buckets challenge"},{"pid":"dcddab6ff77da2a092329873c0a3b81b53fe5a68","tid":691963,"uid":44412,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"1b66cd1344d9055c7a4f2eb82a348cab394a6eea","tid":691963,"uid":147146,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T08:08:18.000Z","msg":"呢個樣 難怪唔夠數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T08:13:25.000Z","msg":"會窮"},{"pid":"b50d34e08089e34c6291dadb35dca08cfc3e4d3b","tid":691963,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T08:15:16.000Z","msg":"用多少少錢改造下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1f649d5fd021856ef884e09bff0b39e9d1cc276","tid":691963,"uid":73262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1b66cd1344d9055c7a4f2eb82a348cab394a6eea","tid":691963,"uid":147146,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T08:08:18.000Z","msg":"呢個樣 難怪唔夠數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T08:17:38.000Z","msg":"靚嘅  上司點都俾夠數佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af3d908bc5826904f2a9d2540dc08dbaed4a3bc6","tid":691963,"uid":95,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T08:18:36.000Z","msg":"白痴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 明明只係公司既一粒齒輪"},{"pid":"0d4e360b1f2e1c3dca85ceeddaf71f66871ef7bb","tid":691963,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T08:23:34.000Z","msg":"共產黨員為地產公司跑數，大嗌堅持完成<br />\n有種不可言喻嘅感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}